$h3 Reflow Maven skin 1.4 Release Notes
**2018-10-05**

$h4 Minor enhancements

- Add ability to explicitly load custom Velocity tools
- If "publishDate position" is set to "none" also exclude the generation date from the automatically generated comment in the header [Pull Request #24][PR-24] ([chrisdutz](https://github.com/chrisdutz)).
- Add auto-adjust placement of sub dropdown menu when out of window.

$h4 Bug fixes

- Fix missing highlightjs javascript call

[PR-24]: https://github.com/devacfr/reflow-maven-skin/pull/24

$h3 Reflow Maven skin 1.3 Release Notes
**2017-12-01**

$h4 Minor enhancements

- Update JQuery version to 3.3.1
- Update Bootstrap version to 3.3.7
- Update LightBox version to 2.10.0
- Add affix on toc side bar.
- Change groupId to io.github.devacfr to deploy on maven central repository.
- Add CI on master branch
- Add AnchorJs javascript library.
- Exclude heading in carousel section(s) for TOC bar and sidebar.
- Add gpg signature,
- Remove white space in generate html.
- Double 'well' in TOC is fixed [Pull request #11](https://github.com/devacfr/reflow-maven-skin/pull/8) (Maxim Solodovnik <solomax666@gmail.com>).
- Sidebar should be hidden for small devices [Pull request #8](https://github.com/devacfr/reflow-maven-skin/pull/8) (Maxim Solodovnik <solomax666@gmail.com>).

$h4 Bug fixes

- TOC block overlapping carousel element ([#23][]).
- Fix jquery error: jquery.min.js:2 Uncaught Error: Syntax error, unrecognized expression: #
- Fix the method fixTableHeads (for Tag List Report), now convert table containing only one head row.
- Second level menu on mobile devices #20 (Maxim Solodovnik <solomax666@gmail.com>).
- In checkstyle report link on detail of file doesn't work.
- Can not click on breadcrumb.
- Fix Top navbar overlaps with header.
- Fix scroll to Top.
- Fix url project in copyright.

[#23]: ${issue-url}/23

